WEBVTT

07:00.964 --> 07:02.214
Don't they live a life filled with pride?

07:02.839 --> 07:04.214
You must be like them.

07:05.131 --> 07:06.089
Did you get it?

07:07.714 --> 07:12.631
My mother was my life and
a scoundrel took her away from me.

07:13.214 --> 07:14.881
I don't know where he is.

07:15.506 --> 07:18.839
But the moment I find him, I'll behead him.
